Package: hiddenmeta
Type: Package
Title: Meta-analysis of hidden population studies
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2020-11-20
Author: 
    c(person(given = "Georgiy", family = "Syunyaev", email = "gs2716@columbia.edu",
             role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person(given = "Macartan", family = "Humphreys", email = "macartan@gmail.com",
             role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Georgiy Syunyaev <gs2716@columbia.edu>
Description: Helper functions for individual and multi study RDS, TLS and proportional sampling from hidden populations and size estimation. 
    The functions allow for easy declaration of one or more studies
    with various design features. In addition, package provides functions for meta-analysis of
    performance comparison of various estimation methods based on RDS and proportional sampling.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
